               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380917-name-134" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380917-name-134" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380917-name-134" type="surname" value="PAGE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380917-name-134" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN PAGE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a shoemaker, and live in Hampstead-road. On the 17th of August, about half-past nine o'clock in the evening, I saw the prisoner take these shoes from my window, put them under his jacket, and walk away with them—I pursued him, and just as I was going to lay hold of him, he threw them at my feet, and ran away—I caught him again, without losing sight of him, and gave him in charge—these are my shoes—(<hi rend="italic">looking at them</hi>.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380917-name-135" type="witnessName">
