                        <interp inst="t18380917-name-135" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT TURNER</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in the neighbourhood. I saw Mr. Page run<lb></lb>ning after a boy, and saw him throw the shoes down when Mr. Page got near him—I cannot swear to the boy.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
